  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "Margaret was collecting her mother's working materials, and preparing to\ngo to bed. Just as she was leaving the room, she hesitated—she was\ninclined to make an acknowledgment which she thought would please her\nfather, but which to be full and true must include a little annoyance.\nHowever, out it came."
  },
