  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "Mr. Horsfall took him a little on one side, as Margaret conjectured, to\nask him some other question about the strike; but, in truth, it was to\ninquire who she herself was—so quiet, so stately, and so beautiful."
