  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "'How came he into the Union?' asked Margaret innocently. 'You don't seem\nto have much respect for him; nor gained much good from having him in.'"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "Higgins's brow clouded. He was silent for a minute or two. Then he said,\nshortly enough:"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
