    "innerHtml": "'But yours is factory slang.'"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "'And if I live in a factory town, I must speak factory language when I\nwant it. Why, mamma, I could astonish you with a great many words you\nnever heard in your life. I don't believe you know what a knobstick is.'"
  },
