  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "At the time arranged the previous day, they set out on their walk to see\nNicholas Higgins and his daughter. They both were reminded of their\nrecent loss, by a strange kind of shyness in their new habiliments, and\nin the fact that it was the first time, for many weeks, that they had\ndeliberately gone out together. They drew very close to each other in\nunspoken sympathy."
  },
  {
