  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "'Sit ye down, sit ye down. Fire's welly out,' said he, giving it a\nvigorous poke, as if to turn attention away from himself. He was rather\ndisorderly, to be sure, with a black unshaven beard of several days'\ngrowth, making his pale face look yet paler, and a jacket which would\nhave been all the better for patching."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "'We thought we should have a good chance of finding you, just after\ndinner-time,' said Margaret."
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
